sentences: Priti Paintal (born 1960) is an East Indian composer, performer, music producer and promoter who lives and works in England.
She founded the ensemble ShivaNova in 1988 to unite diverse musical traditions into a global sound.
A mainstream dance music spin-off of the group, SugarNova, had its debut single "Over and Over" reach the top 20 of the Music Week Club charts.
She has appeared on Songlines, BBC 3 and Woman's Hour.
